fromMaybe | Just | Nothing : Maybe
Either :: Either
Maybe :: Maybe
IO
---

This is an example of the basics.

It has headmatter content which allows for dynamic imports.

We can define some stuff here:

  hundred = Just(100)
  bad = Nothing

And now let's do something with those imports:

  pipe(
    fromMaybe(33),
    IO.pTrace("outputs!")
  )(bad)
